   "ObjectType" -> "Symbol", "Usage" -> 
    "GammaMatrices[n] returns n Euclidean gamma matrices of dimension \
2^Floor[n/2] in the Brauer\[Dash]Weyl (Pauli\[Dash]Kronecker) representation.\
\nGammaMatrices[\[Eta]] returns gamma matrices satisfying the Clifford \
relation {\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[Gamma]\), \
\(\[Mu]\)]\),\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[Gamma]\), \(\[Nu]\)]\)} = \
2\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[Eta]\), \(\[Mu]\[Nu]\)]\) \[DoubleStruckCapitalI] \
for any real symmetric metric \[Eta]. For a flat diagonal metric of signature \
(p,q) the result is \[ImaginaryI] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalGamma]\), \
\(\[Mu]\)]\) for time-like indices and \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalGamma]\
\), \(\[Mu]\)]\) for space-like indices; for a general metric a vielbein \
decomposition is used.", "Documentation" -> None, "OwnValues" -> None, 
    "UpValues" -> None, "DownValues" -> 
    Information`InformationValueForm[
     DownValues, DiracMatrix`GammaMatrices, {DiracMatrix`GammaMatrices[
         PatternTest[
          Pattern[DiracMatrix`Private`n, 
           Blank[Integer]], Positive]] :> 
       DiracMatrix`EuclideanGammaMatrices[DiracMatrix`Private`n], Condition[
         DiracMatrix`GammaMatrices[
          PatternTest[
           Pattern[DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta], 
            Blank[]], DiagonalMatrixQ]], 
         ContainsOnly[
          Diagonal[DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta]], {-1, 1}]] :> Diagonal[
          ReplaceAll[DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta], {-1 :> I}]] 
        DiracMatrix`EuclideanGammaMatrices[
          Length[DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta]]], DiracMatrix`GammaMatrices[
         Condition[
          Pattern[DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta], 
           Blank[]], 
          SymmetricMatrixQ[
          DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta], Tolerance -> 10^(-12)]]] :> 
       Module[{DiracMatrix`Private`signature, DiracMatrix`Private`vielbein, 
          DiracMatrix`Private`\[CapitalGamma]flat}, {
           DiracMatrix`Private`signature, DiracMatrix`Private`vielbein} = 
          DiracMatrix`MetricVielbein[DiracMatrix`Private`\[Eta]]; 
         DiracMatrix`Private`\[CapitalGamma]flat = 
          DiracMatrix`GammaMatrices[DiracMatrix`Private`signature]; 
         TensorContract[
           TensorProduct[
           DiracMatrix`Private`vielbein, 
            DiracMatrix`Private`\[CapitalGamma]flat], {{1, 3}}]]}], 
    "SubValues" -> None, "DefaultValues" -> None, "NValues" -> None, 
    "FormatValues" -> None, "Options" -> None, "Attributes" -> {}, "FullName" -> 
    "DiracMatrix`GammaMatrices"|>, False]]], "Output",
